166
00:17:33,248 --> 00:17:34,416
But I’m going to do it.

167
00:17:35,648 --> 00:17:37,648
I’ve decided to become a cop.

168
00:17:38,464 --> 00:17:40,224
If I ignore this,

169
00:17:41,152 --> 00:17:42,928
I won’t deserve to be called a police officer.

170
00:17:49,344 --> 00:17:50,496
Then I’ll do it too.

171
00:17:53,872 --> 00:17:56,240
If he’s in then I’m also in.

172
00:17:57,840 --> 00:17:58,992
Me too.

